# ./benchmark
testing: BBC WHP031 RS(15, 11) T=2
encoding of 10000000 random bytes (1818182 blocks) took 249 milliseconds (40161KB/s).
checking of 13636365 encoded bytes (1818182 blocks) took 237 milliseconds (57537KB/s).
decoding of 13636365 encoded bytes with 3636364 errors took 814 milliseconds (16752KB/s).
testing: DVB-T RS(255, 239) T=8
encoding of 10000000 random bytes (41842 blocks) took 195 milliseconds (51282KB/s).
checking of 10669710 encoded bytes (41842 blocks) took 385 milliseconds (27714KB/s).
decoding of 10669710 encoded bytes with 334736 errors took 625 milliseconds (17072KB/s).
testing: FUN RS(65535, 65471) T=32
encoding of 10000000 random bytes (77 blocks) took 457 milliseconds (21882KB/s).
checking of 10092390 encoded bytes (77 blocks) took 1033 milliseconds (9770KB/s).
decoding of 10092390 encoded bytes with 2464 errors took 1472 milliseconds (6856KB/s).
